WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.710
Hey, good morning family, or

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:04.789
afternoon, or evening, or good night, or

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:07.590
wherever you are in the world. I have

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:08.870
some things I want to talk to you

00:00:08.870 --> 00:00:08.880
all

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:11.589
about. If you go back to the word I gave

00:00:11.589 --> 00:00:11.599
ten

00:00:11.599 --> 00:00:15.270
months ago or

00:00:15.270 --> 00:00:15.280
more—it’s

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:17.990
probably about a year or so ago

00:00:17.990 --> 00:00:18.000
now—whenever

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:21.189
the Lord showed me the dollar crashing.

00:00:21.189 --> 00:00:21.199
I’m

00:00:21.199 --> 00:00:23.349
going to go over that again.

00:00:23.359 --> 00:00:26.870
He warned me that

00:00:26.870 --> 00:00:26.880
there’s

00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:30.349
going to be a major

00:00:30.359 --> 00:00:34.229
global shaking of finances,

00:00:34.239 --> 00:00:36.950
bringing forth digital platforms.

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:39.190
This is what he told me about a year

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:43.430
ago. I was praying and I saw a flagpole

00:00:43.430 --> 00:00:43.440
with

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:47.750
a $100 bill on

00:00:47.750 --> 00:00:47.760
it.

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:51.270
It was moving back and forth, and I

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:55.350
saw digital writing. It

00:00:55.360 --> 00:00:59.590
looked like digital code in this $100

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:01.590
bill, and it was alive and moving,

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:03.590
kind of like stocks, but it was

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:06.710
digital. It was like crypto

00:01:06.710 --> 00:01:06.720
writing.

00:01:06.720 --> 00:01:08.070
Do you know what

00:01:08.070 --> 00:01:08.080
I’m

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:09.990
talking about, son? Okay, so it was

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:13.910
moving like that. Then I

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:15.590
said, "Lord, what are you showing

00:01:15.590 --> 00:01:15.600
me?"And

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:18.390
he said, "The dollar is about to

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:21.910
turn into a digital dollar, and it will

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:25.350
be worth half of

00:01:25.350 --> 00:01:25.360
the

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:27.590
purchasing power of what it used

00:01:27.600 --> 00:01:30.950
to be."I saw it was at 50

00:01:30.950 --> 00:01:30.960
cents—purchasing

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:35.590
power of 50 cents to a

00:01:35.590 --> 00:01:35.600
dollar—because

00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:37.910
of inflation

00:01:37.910 --> 00:01:37.920
and

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:40.069
the things happening with

00:01:40.079 --> 00:01:42.510
America and the

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:46.310
economy.

00:01:49.439 --> 00:01:53.350
Then he showed me what was going to happen: the banking

00:01:53.360 --> 00:01:56.310
sector. All the major banks—Chase Bank,

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:59.830
Wells Fargo, you name it, the huge world

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:00.630
banks—all

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:05.190
seized the money inside of the

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:09.109
banks. It was like it went into a

00:02:09.109 --> 00:02:09.119
bail-in.

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:12.390
I don't know what you

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:14.550
would call that. Like I said, I'm

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:16.710
not real educated on stuff like this.

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:19.190
I saw all the money being seized

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:21.670
inside of the banks, and you weren't

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:24.150
allowed to withdraw any of

00:02:24.150 --> 00:02:24.160
it.

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.790
People were furious

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:27.750
because they couldn't get their

00:02:27.760 --> 00:02:30.390
money out; the banks

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:34.630
kept it. When

00:02:34.640 --> 00:02:35.910
this happened, the dollar crashed.

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:39.110
Then they took

00:02:39.110 --> 00:02:39.120
all

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:41.589
the

00:02:41.599 --> 00:02:44.150
notes on the homes

00:02:44.150 --> 00:02:44.160
and

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:46.470
the

00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:48.390
car loans, everything, because people

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:50.150
couldn't make their payments anymore

00:02:50.150 --> 00:02:50.160
since

00:02:50.160 --> 00:02:53.350
the dollar had collapsed. I

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:57.110
saw people's car notes and car loans

00:02:57.120 --> 00:03:00.309
wiped out, kind of like

00:03:00.319 --> 00:03:03.110
it was with

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:06.229
student

00:03:06.239 --> 00:03:08.550
loans back whenever the big

00:03:08.550 --> 00:03:08.560
COVID

00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:11.509
happened. They weren't allowed to

00:03:11.509 --> 00:03:11.519
collect

00:03:11.519 --> 00:03:14.470
those student loans;

00:03:14.480 --> 00:03:17.589
they froze all that for

00:03:17.599 --> 00:03:21.550
several years, and people weren't made

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:24.630
to pay those payments anymore.

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.390
That's what it was like with the

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:29.670
housing market or the car loans. They

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:32.229
didn't come and foreclose on everybody.

00:03:32.239 --> 00:03:33.670
They didn't say, "Hey, you're

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:35.270
out."They

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:37.910
just froze it across the board because

00:03:37.920 --> 00:03:39.430
they didn't make everybody make their

00:03:39.440 --> 00:03:41.509
payments, just like it was with student

00:03:41.519 --> 00:03:44.550
loans. That's what I saw; I

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:46.830
did not see any more of what happened

00:03:46.830 --> 00:03:46.840
afterward.

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:49.030
People say, "Well, this

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:51.190
is a debt jubilee."I didn't see it like

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:52.789
that. That's what I'm trying to say. I

00:03:52.799 --> 00:03:55.270
don't want to add anything to or take

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:58.070
anything away from this prophetic

00:03:58.080 --> 00:03:59.830
word. I just want to tell you what the

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.229
Lord showed me. Then the Lord

00:04:02.239 --> 00:04:04.309
showed me people who were dressed

00:04:04.309 --> 00:04:04.319
up.

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:06.710
Because it happened so quickly—kind of

00:04:06.720 --> 00:04:08.949
like I told you all about the four oak

00:04:08.949 --> 00:04:08.959
trees—if

00:04:08.959 --> 00:04:11.750
you go back to the prophetic

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:14.070
word that I gave, the dream I had

00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:16.949
about the four oak trees, four years or

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:19.509
four months or four whatever it was,

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:22.629
each oak tree

00:04:22.639 --> 00:04:24.950
represented, I believe, a year. Now,

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:27.510
some people say it's a season because of

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:29.350
what I saw, and some people say it is

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:30.550
whatever. It's your

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:32.950
interpretation. I just told you all to

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:34.710
pray about it and see what the Holy

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:38.790
Spirit tells you concerning

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:40.550
these things that the Lord shows me,

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:42.150
because I see in part and hear

00:04:42.150 --> 00:04:42.160
in

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:44.150
part, and I'm a work

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:46.230
in progress just like everybody else.

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:47.990
But if the Lord's telling me to tell you

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.510
something, I want you to pray about

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:51.270
it and see what he's telling

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:54.790
you. I saw people in nice clothes

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:56.150
because it happened just like I told

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:57.749
you; it happened like winter came

00:04:57.759 --> 00:04:59.430
onto the trees, they lost all their

00:04:59.440 --> 00:05:01.189
