00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:05.909
People were standing in line

00:05:05.919 --> 00:05:08.469
trying to find groceries. They were

00:05:08.479 --> 00:05:11.670
trying to get groceries at the

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:13.830
store, but there was no food.

00:05:13.840 --> 00:05:16.469
Remember I told you

00:05:16.479 --> 00:05:18.790
