00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.950
I could see cobwebs in the corners

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:23.430
of these shelves in the grocery stores,

00:05:23.440 --> 00:05:26.710
which I believe represented

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:29.749
quite some time passing, because

00:05:29.759 --> 00:05:32.550
cobwebs don't happen in the

00:05:32.550 --> 00:05:32.560
corners of

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:34.790
a grocery store shelf unless

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:36.870
it's over time. It doesn't happen

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:37.990
overnight.

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:39.990
There were shelves that were

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:43.189
completely bare in these grocery stores.

00:05:43.199 --> 00:05:45.909
People were lined up trying to

00:05:45.919 --> 00:05:48.550
get whatever they could in paper

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:50.710
sacks or whatever they had, but

00:05:50.720 --> 00:05:52.230
like I said, they had nice

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:54.390
